AMAX Incx said it has identifiedadditional gold and silver ore reserves at its AMAX SleeperMine near Winnemucca, Nev..    It said as a result of recent drilling, reserves at thhemine are now estimated at 2,470,000 short tons of ore grading0.24 ounce of gold and 0.50 ounce of silver per ton that istreatable by conventional milling techniques.    AMAX said additional reserves amenable to heap leaching areestimated at 38.3 mln tons averaging 0.025 ounce gold and 0.24ounce silver per ton.  Further drilling is being conducted, itsaid. Reuter&#3;